data.description: Motivated Sellers! Come take a look! Here is a great, spacious home in the beautiful subdivision of Terrace Meadows! Five bedrooms, 2.5 baths, two additional living spaces, and a dining room will give you plenty of room to roam! The house sits on a beautiful lot with just over a half acre with mature trees and a fenced in back yard along with two gazebos. This home is a must see and has tons of potential for you to make it your own!
